{"id":"guide/i18n-common-locale-id","title":"Refer to locales by ID","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-locale-id.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"refer-to-locales-by-id\" translation-result=\"on\">透過 ID 參考語言環境<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id#refer-to-locales-by-id\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Refer to locales by ID<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id#refer-to-locales-by-id\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 使用 Unicode <em>語言環境識別符號</em>（Unicode 語言環境 ID）來查詢正確的語言環境資料，以實現文字字串的國際化。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular uses the Unicode <em>locale identifier</em> (Unicode locale ID) to find the correct locale data for internationalization of text strings.</p>\n\n<div class=\"callout is-helpful\">\n<header ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">Unicode 語言環境 ID</header><header ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Unicode locale ID</header>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">語言環境 ID 遵循 <a href=\"https://cldr.unicode.org/development/core-specification\" title=\"Core Specification | Unicode CLDR Project\">Unicode 通用語言環境資料儲存庫 (CLDR) 核心規範</a>。有關語言環境 ID 的更多資訊，請參閱 <a href=\"https://cldr.unicode.org/development/core-specification#h.vgyyng33o798\" title=\"Unicode Language and Locale Identifiers - Core Specification | Unicode CLDR Project\">Unicode 語言和語言環境識別符號</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A locale ID conforms to the <a href=\"https://cldr.unicode.org/development/core-specification\" title=\"Core Specification | Unicode CLDR Project\">Unicode Common Locale Data Repository (CLDR) core specification</a>.\nFor more information about locale IDs, see <a href=\"https://cldr.unicode.org/development/core-specification#h.vgyyng33o798\" title=\"Unicode Language and Locale Identifiers - Core Specification | Unicode CLDR Project\">Unicode Language and Locale Identifiers</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">CLDR 和 Angular 以 <a href=\"https://www.rfc-editor.org/info/bcp47\" title=\"BCP 47 | RFC Editor\">BCP 47 標籤</a> 作為語言環境 ID 的基礎。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">CLDR and Angular use <a href=\"https://www.rfc-editor.org/info/bcp47\" title=\"BCP 47 | RFC Editor\">BCP 47 tags</a> as the base for the locale ID</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">語言環境 ID 指定語言、國家/地區和其他變體或細分的可選程式碼。語言環境 ID 由語言識別符號、破折號（<code>-</code>）字元和語言環境擴充組成。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A locale ID specifies the language, country, and an optional code for further variants or subdivisions.\nA locale ID consists of the language identifier, a hyphen (<code>-</code>) character, and the locale extension.</p>\n\n<code-example>\n\n{language_id}-{locale_extension}\n\n</code-example>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">為了準確地翻譯你的 Angular 專案，你必須決定你的國際化目標語言和地區。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To accurately translate your Angular project, you must decide which languages and locales you are targeting for internationalization.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">許多國家使用相同的語言，但用法上有些差異。這些差異包括語法、標點符號、貨幣格式、十進位制數字、日期等。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Many countries share the same language, but differ in usage.\nThe differences include grammar, punctuation, formats for currency, decimal numbers, dates, and so on.</p>\n\n</div>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">對於本指南中的範例，使用瞭如下語言和語言環境。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For the examples in this guide, use the following languages and locales.</p>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">語言</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Language</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">地區</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Locale</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">Unicode 語言環境 ID</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Unicode locale ID</nt-wrapper></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">英語</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">English</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">加拿大</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Canada</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>en-CA</code></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">英語</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">English</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">美國</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">United States of America</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>en-US</code></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">法語</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">French</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">加拿大</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Canada</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>fr-CA</code></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">法語</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">French</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">法國</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">France</nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>fr-FR</code></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/main/packages/common/locales\" title=\"angular/packages/common/locales | angular/angular | GitHub\">Angular 程式碼儲存庫</a>中包括常見的一些語言環境。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/main/packages/common/locales\" title=\"angular/packages/common/locales | angular/angular | GitHub\">Angular repository</a> includes common locales.</p>\n\n<div class=\"callout is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有關語言程式碼列表，請參閱 <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/standards/iso639-2\" title=\"ISO 639-2 Registration Authority | Library of Congress\">ISO 639-2</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For a list of language codes, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/standards/iso639-2\" title=\"ISO 639-2 Registration Authority | Library of Congress\">ISO 639-2</a>.</p>\n\n<!--todo: Is this accurate.  ISO 639-2 is 3 digit.  ISO 639-1 is 2 digit.  Reference: http://www.loc.gov/standards/iso639-2/php/code_list.php -->\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"set-the-source-locale-id\" translation-result=\"on\">設定源語言環境 ID<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id#set-the-source-locale-id\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Set the source locale ID<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id#set-the-source-locale-id\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 Angular CLI 設定編寫元件範本和程式碼所用的源語言。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the Angular CLI to set the source language in which you are writing the component template and code.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">預設情況下，Angular 使用 <code>en-US</code> 作為專案的源語言環境。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">By default, Angular uses <code>en-US</code> as the source locale of your project.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要為此建構更改專案的源語言環境，請完成以下操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To change the source locale of your project for the build, complete the following actions.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">開啟工作空間建構配置檔案 <a href=\"guide/workspace-config\" title=\"Angular workspace configuration | Angular\"><code>angular.json</code></a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Open the <a href=\"guide/workspace-config\" title=\"Angular workspace configuration | Angular\"><code>angular.json</code></a> workspace build configuration file.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 <code>sourceLocale</code> 欄位中更改源語言環境。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Change the source locale in the <code>sourceLocale</code> field.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" translation-result=\"on\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">What's next<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" title=\"Format data based on locale | Angular\">根據語言環境格式化資料</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" title=\"Format data based on locale | Angular\">Format data based on locale</a></p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：10/28/2021</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/PercentPipe\n - api/core/DEFAULT_CURRENCY_CODE\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id#refer-to-locales-by-id\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id#set-the-source-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id#whats-next\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id#下一步呢\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id#設定源語言環境-id\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id#透過-id-參考語言環境\n - guide/workspace-config\n - https://cldr.unicode.org/development/core-specification\n - https://cldr.unicode.org/development/core-specification#h.vgyyng33o798\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/main/packages/common/locales\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-locale-id.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://www.loc.gov/standards/iso639-2\n - https://www.rfc-editor.org/info/bcp47\n-->"}